playlists.description: Welcome to Party Royale, an experimental and evolving space. Leave your weapons and mats behind and hang out with friends, play games and enjoy live entertainment. Catch live shows. Race around obstacle courses by land or sea. Go fishing with friends, perfect your skydive, and get up close and connect with some of your favorite artists. Hop on the party bus and enjoy the ride.
Matchmake with others and play the best games made by the community!
Go at it alone in a battle to be the last one standing.
Pair up with a buddy and take everyone else down.
Group up and outlast all of the other squads gunning for victory.
